      <title>富时推迟将韩国和印度纳入主要债券指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/ftse-holds-off-adding-south-korea-india-to-key-bond-indexes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富时罗素表示，韩国将继续留在其全球债券指数的观察名单上——和印度相当于新兴市场——再次将这些国家加入关键指数的时间再推迟至少六个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/ftse-holds-off-adding-south-korea-india-to-key-bond-indexes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着跨山开始临近，加拿大石油流向洛杉矶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/canadian-oil-flows-to-los-angeles-as-trans-mountain-start-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大向洛杉矶的原油运输量正在激增，这可能预示着即将启动的扩建管道将如何重新吸引太平洋沿岸的流量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/canadian-oil-flows-to-los-angeles-as-trans-mountain-start-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房地产公司 Adler 希望以高达 47% 的折扣出售资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/property-firm-adler-looks-to-sell-assets-at-up-to-47-discount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adler Group SA 请求其债券持有人允许以比不到两年前的估值低 47% 的价格出售未完工的公寓开发项目，因为这家陷入困境的房东竞相偿还巨额债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/property-firm-adler-looks-to-sell-assets-at-up-to-47-discount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施莱格尔表示，瑞士央行没有设定法郎汇率目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/snb-has-no-target-for-franc-exchange-rate-schlegel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行副行长马丁·施莱格尔表示，瑞士央行没有设定瑞郎汇率目标。不到一周前，瑞士央行决策者通过降息以遏制瑞郎升值，导致市场措手不及。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/snb-has-no-target-for-franc-exchange-rate-schlegel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卖空者的获胜赌注意味着向杰富瑞永久付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/short-seller-s-winning-bet-means-permanent-payments-to-jefferies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家做空一家陷入困境的零售连锁店的卖空者声称，它现在正在付出代价：每月向杰富瑞集团无休止地付款，十多年前，杰富瑞集团就借给了它股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/short-seller-s-winning-bet-means-permanent-payments-to-jefferies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称股市过于拥挤，随时可能崩盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/jpmorgan-says-crowded-stocks-sow-risk-of-out-of-the-blue-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是股市的热门话题：美国股市五个月的涨势即将结束的迹象是什么。但如果你问摩根大通公司的杜布拉夫科·拉科斯-布哈斯，投资者可能不会预见到它的到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/jpmorgan-says-crowded-stocks-sow-risk-of-out-of-the-blue-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:11:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于电视前景恶化，派拉蒙债务被削减至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级公司将派拉蒙全球公司的债务评级下调至垃圾级，该评级机构称，由于该公司的广播和有线电视业务持续下滑，现金流面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究称，Novo 售价 1,000 美元的糖尿病药物 Ozempic 每月的生产成本不到 5 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/ozempic-novo-s-1-000-diabetes-drug-can-be-made-for-less-than-5-a-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项研究表明，即使制造商诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 在美国的收费近 1,000 美元，Ozempic 的生产成本每月不到 5 美元，但该研究再次引发了人们对最畅销的糖尿病和肥胖症治疗药物价格的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/ozempic-novo-s-1-000-diabetes-drug-can-be-made-for-less-than-5-a-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官裁定 SEC 针对 Coinbase 的诉讼可以继续进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/sec-suit-against-coinbase-can-go-forward-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约一名联邦法官裁定，美国证券交易委员会可以继续对美国最大的加密货币交易平台 Coinbase Inc. 提起诉讼，称该公司未能注册为证券公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/sec-suit-against-coinbase-can-go-forward-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
